<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. La'n sa'ng ka thusim maktak chu,
 Krista kei ding a thi chu;
 A In nuomtak chu taihsan a,
 Kalvari a A thih chu.

[V2]
 La'n sa'ng ka thusim maktak chu,
 Krista kei ding a thi chu;
 Lopi mithiengte tawh sa'i tiu,
 Luigal a I kikhawp tieng.

[V3]
 2. A beimangsa Isu'n ei mu'i,
 Belam taimangsa ei mu'i;
 A hehpih khut a ei pawm in,
 Amah lam ah ei puita'i.

[V4]
 3. Ka liemna Isu'n ei hihdam,
 Lau leh thingilh a um kha;
 Mu theilo in lauhna'n ka dim,
 Ei hihveng lauhum apat.

[V5]
 4. Nicheng' thim in ei khuh zing hi,
 Lam lauhum a ka um in;
 Mahleh Lalpa'n ei umpih zing,
 A ban thahat in ei pui.

[V6]
 5. Luipi lien ah ei veng intin,
 Tuilien a kan macheng chu;
 Bit takin ei pui kai intin,
 Ziechun lungdeihte tuok ka.</lyrics>
<title>I WILL SING THE WONDROUS STORY</title>
<hymn_number>39</hymn_number>
</song>